QuestData.Title: Prospectus Bay
QuestData.Description:
Looks like we made it in unnoticed.
Skaggit's crew can set up shop on that beach, but we gotta make sure it's safe for 'em to land first.
Let's do a quick flyover to scout out how we're going to crack this place wide open.
That town up on the hill looks promising...
QuestData.LogDescription: Jetpack into Prospectus Bay with Gazlowe and the crew.
